    "text": "TCGrena Games You don't have any games loaded yet. Add some here. Decks Play Preferences Custom games - BETA Discord Support Login America server is now available. An easy to use simulator for all your favorite TCGs Build decks and play with up to 3 other players. Features Play Play with your friends for free to any game made by the community on a Chrome or Firefox browser, no accounts needed! Up to 4 players. Create games Can't find the game you want to play ? TCG Arena is not built around a specific game. It loads highly customizable game files that anybody can make and share with their friends. Build Build decks with our deckbuilder or quickly import them from your favorite deckbuilding tool. Our deckbuilder is run locally with all the latest cards data, allowing search filters to be built automatically on the go and always up to date. Automatization The app is not made to implement card effects. But games can use mutliple options to automatize some core actions like paying ressource cost or placing cards played in the right area. Keep track Visual links between cards, pinging your opponent cards, ... Lots of features to help you show your opponents what you want to do, just like you would do when playing around a table. Support The app is and will always remain free to use. If you want to help with the server cost, you can support TCG Arena on KoFi. Supporters have access to the sleeves customization that let you wrap cards in a colorful background and an image of your choice. TCG Arena is not affiliated with, endorsed, sponsored, or specifically approved by any TCG playable on it. No artworks or game material used by games on this platform belong to TCG Arena. No TCGs are hosted on this platform, the Game tab is only here to offer you a quick acces to the link hosting files for those games. If you have made files using the game builder and want a link to them on this page let me know on Discord. More in our Privacy policy. This is a free educational tool, it does not include tournaments or rankings. All features are accessible for free and are not intended for commercial use. This app is still a work in progress, if you have issues or suggestions, feel free to reach me on Discord. Current version 1.27.1 App icon by Md Tanvirul Haque, other icons by Freepik. Homepage and login image by Zishan Liu. Cards 1 and 5 from the homepage by wia.",
