    "text": "MAINTENANCE NOTICE Maintenance starts in 4 hours 25 minutes. New games, deck creation, and deck editing will be disabled 30 minutes before that time, and running games may disconnect during the maintenance window. PLAY.RIFTATLAS Lobby Paste your deck first, then host or join with a room code. Sign in Sign up Contact Join the Discord Buy me a coffee LEGEND 0/1 CHAMPION 0/1 MAIN DECK 0/39 BATTLEFIELDS 0/3 RUNES 0/12 SIDEBOARD 0/0 Paste a deck LEGEND No legend. CHAMPION No champion. MAIN DECK No main deck cards. SIDEBOARD No sideboard. BATTLEFIELDS No battlefields. RUNES No runes. IMPORT DECK NEW DECK CHOOSE DECK SAVE DECK PLAYER Shown to opponents PLAY MODE CONSTRUCTED UNLEASHED PRE-RIFT MATCH FORMAT BEST OF 1 BEST OF 3 QUICK MATCH FIND RANDOM MATCH Include Unleashed decks CREATE ROOM HOST ROOM JOIN WITH CODE JOIN ROOM Play.Riftatlas is an unofficial fan project for Riftbound: League of Legends Trading Card Game. It uses Riot Games-owned IP under Riot Games' \"Legal Jibber Jabber\" policy. Riot Games does not endorse or sponsor this project. Privacy Policy Terms of Service Contact",
